name: foggy evening 😶‍🌫️
description: The fog thickened before you could realize it had even started. In under five minutes, despite being in a well known area and feeling like you moved only carefully, you were completely unable to tell where your own feet were situated. Furthermore, in spite of your partial blindness to the world around, you noticed that the surroundings seemed to have strangely changed to a place you definitely had never seen before...
